1
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:26,880
Fan, scum like Han Qi

2
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:28,560
would do anything for money.

3
00:01:29,080 --> 00:01:30,920
He even laid his hands
on a century-old cemetery.

4
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:32,520
Why are you working with him?

5
00:01:32,720 --> 00:01:33,360
Have you forgotten

6
00:01:33,360 --> 00:01:35,759
how you taught him
a lesson here 3 years ago?

7
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:42,000
Mr. Lu.

8
00:01:42,720 --> 00:01:43,440
Speak.

9
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:46,160
Mr. Lu, the Han family is dropping

10
00:01:46,160 --> 00:01:47,160
the cemetery development project.

11
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:48,600
I'll shut it down immediately.

12
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:49,800
No, that's not right.

13
00:01:50,520 --> 00:01:52,000
Say "development plan."

14
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:54,039
W-We're dropping the development plan.

15
00:01:54,039 --> 00:01:54,800
It's off.

16
00:02:00,240 --> 00:02:02,240
I'll speak. I'll speak

17
00:02:02,360 --> 00:02:04,480
The cemetery is holding back
the suburban development project.

18
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:07,810
The cemetery needs to be relocated,
and the graves exhumed.

19
00:02:13,440 --> 00:02:15,440
Do you know why cornered prey

20
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:16,570
is the most frantic?

21
00:02:18,440 --> 00:02:20,079
Because what they're
holding onto isn't a lifeline.

22
00:02:20,079 --> 00:02:21,040
It's a noose.

23
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:26,120
Neither of us can find Su Xia.

24
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:28,280
But he can.

25
00:02:33,480 --> 00:02:35,640
Is there anything you won't do

26
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:37,560
to get Su Xia back?

27
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:41,560
Mr. Lu,

28
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:42,520
the cemetery staff said

29
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:44,760
someone scheduled a visit
to Mr. Su's grave today.

30
00:02:44,760 --> 00:02:45,560
Got it.

31
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:51,720
Recently, Lu Fan, CEO of the Lu Group,

32
00:02:51,720 --> 00:02:53,200
and Jian Xi, daughter of the Jian Group

33
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:54,760
announced their engagement.

34
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:55,820
As everyone knows,

35
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,640
three years ago, Lu Group

36
00:02:57,640 --> 00:02:59,160
was involved in a scandal.

37
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:01,840
Lu Fan has become a legend

38
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:03,720
in the business world.

39
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:05,480
He turned the company around

40
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:08,540
and brought the Lu Group back
to its peak in just 3 years.

41
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:12,400
Do you think what happened
3 years ago was true,

42
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,280
or just a rumor?

43
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:17,680
Lu Fan.

44
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:20,250
If you just wanted
to force me to come back,

45
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:21,400
it worked.

46
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:39,560
Mr. Xiao.

47
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,840
Why are you here?

48
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:50,780
Did someone in your family pass away?

49
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:54,200
You're as sharp-tongued as ever.

50
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:56,770
I'm in a good mood today,

51
00:03:56,880 --> 00:03:58,140
so I came out for a walk.

52
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:02,640
On a day like this,

53
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:05,880
you're coming to a place like this
for a walk?

54
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:06,720
Good taste.

55
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:09,980
Do you need something, Mr. Lu?

56
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,120
I'm here to invite you

57
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:15,120
to tomorrow's celebration banquet

58
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:17,360
for the development plan.

59
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:21,959
Depends.

60
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:34,240
Mr. Lu, why invite Xiao Qi?

61
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:35,860
He's not the one I invited.

62
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:38,960
Su Xia, hide as you want.

63
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:41,120
I'll be waiting for you.

64
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:50,360
One hour and thirty-nine minutes.

65
00:04:50,520 --> 00:04:51,240
Su Xia,

66
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:53,320
you've set a record for making me wait.

67
00:04:53,320 --> 00:04:54,440
I broke the record?

68
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,580
Should I make it longer next time?

69
00:04:57,840 --> 00:04:59,800
Actually, you didn't have to come back.

70
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:02,000
I can handle this little matter for you.

71
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:08,320
I can't avoid it forever.

72
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,520
Ms. Jian,

73
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:25,440
I guess Fan won't be able to make it.

74
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:30,500
Ever since the Lu family's
wedding banquet 3 years ago,

75
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:35,240
he hasn't appeared at this kind
of occasion since.

76
00:05:37,159 --> 00:05:39,200
The cemetery development project
officially broke ground today.

77
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:41,659
A workaholic like him
will definitely come.

78
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:47,400
Do you know him better or do I?

79
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:51,720
Qin Huai, would it kill you to stay quiet?

80
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:03,320
Su Xia? Why is she here?

81
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:25,200
Fan.

82
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:28,560
You're here.

83
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:33,159
Mr. Xiao, long time no see.

84
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:35,280
And this is?

85
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:37,700
This is the woman
who means the most to me.

86
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:41,380
Then congratulations, Mr. Xiao.

87
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:43,320
Please enjoy yourself, Mr. Xiao.

88
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:44,080
Let's go.

89
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,610
You seem to be in a good mood.

90
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:51,920
Not bad.

91
00:06:58,920 --> 00:07:00,560
Su Xia, Han Qi is inside.

92
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:02,880
The Han and Lu families are cooperating.

93
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:04,520
If you want to keep the cemetery,

94
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:05,840
Han Qi is the key.

95
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:07,690
I'll go meet him.

96
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:15,130
What's your blood type?

97
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:16,720
Type O.

98
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:17,720
Wrong.

99
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:19,400
Then what type?

100
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:21,000
You are my ideal type.

101
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,900
Let me add you on WeChat first.

102
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:24,280
Sure.

103
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:25,920
Okay.

104
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:36,920
Hello, Mr. Han.

105
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:39,000
Why are you here?

106
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:41,730
Don't you recognize me?

107
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:43,480
What do you want?

108
00:07:43,960 --> 00:07:44,760
Easy.

109
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:46,490
I have something to talk to you.

110
00:07:47,760 --> 00:07:50,200
We have nothing to talk about, right?

111
00:07:50,320 --> 00:07:51,280
Relax.

112
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:52,880
I'd like to talk about

113
00:07:52,880 --> 00:07:54,440
the Huishan Cemetery project.

114
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:55,240
For this project,

115
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:56,960
I hope you'll reconsider.

116
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:59,159
I've also put together some thoughts

117
00:07:59,159 --> 00:08:00,120
on this project.

118
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:02,780
I will have someone send them
to you afterwards.

119
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:04,560
Ms. Su.

120
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:07,640
You have to ask Mr. Lu about it.

121
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,260
Aren't you his sister?

122
00:08:09,320 --> 00:08:10,850
That should be easy for you.

123
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:14,240
He's the one really calling the shots
on this project.

124
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:16,000
I am just a nobody.

125
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:17,560
Excuse me, excuse me.

126
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,240
Mr. Han.

127
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:30,080
Youd don't recognize me?

128
00:08:31,880 --> 00:08:32,880
It's been so long.

129
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:35,450
Where have you been hiding?

130
00:08:36,400 --> 00:08:37,280
Still running?

131
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:45,560
You're still putting on the same act.

132
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:50,660
I'll see this game through to the end.

133
00:08:51,880 --> 00:08:53,800
I know you did this to force me back.

134
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:55,040
I came back

135
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:57,220
because I'm not afraid of you.

136
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:04,010
Then why didn't you go to me just now

137
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:04,840
I...

138
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:06,370
but go to Han Qi instead?

139
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:14,890
If you want your father's grave
to stay intact

140
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:17,960
come to the Lu residence tonight.

141
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:21,600
By the way,

142
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:25,480
remember to

143
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,000
beg me nicely.

144
00:10:06,640 --> 00:10:07,760
Do you know what will happen

145
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:08,890
if you go beg him now?

146
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,120
I know.

147
00:10:11,560 --> 00:10:14,240
But this time,
I want to get through it on my own.

148
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:18,000
I just hope you make it out

149
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:23,540
instead of getting sucked in.

150
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:37,360
Thank you, Xiao Qi.

151
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:05,600
Chairman.

152
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,640
Zhen'an, you're here.

153
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:13,480
Why did you ask to meet me here?

154
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:16,160
My creditors are looking
for me everywhere now.

155
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:17,560
Where else can I hide?

156
00:11:18,760 --> 00:11:19,560
Zhen'an.

157
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:22,040
You can still help me, right?

158
00:11:22,680 --> 00:11:23,400
Zhen'an.

159
00:11:24,040 --> 00:11:25,120
You are the CFO.

160
00:11:26,160 --> 00:11:28,120
Can we temporarily use the group's

161
00:11:28,560 --> 00:11:30,160
overseas restricted funds?

162
00:11:30,160 --> 00:11:31,840
I need them to get through this crisis.

163
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:32,900
I'll sign off on it.

164
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:35,100
I can mortgage everything I have.

165
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:37,050
Chairman, have you forgotten?

166
00:11:37,280 --> 00:11:39,960
Three days ago, the board
passed an emergency resolution.

167
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:41,560
Given that your personal debt issues

168
00:11:41,560 --> 00:11:44,320
have seriously
affected the group's reputation,

169
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:46,280
your signing authority

170
00:11:46,560 --> 00:11:48,040
has been temporarily frozen.

171
00:11:48,040 --> 00:11:49,500
As for the overseas funds,

172
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:53,360
touching even a cent of it would violate
cross-border financial regulations.

173
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:54,800
As the head of finance,

174
00:11:54,800 --> 00:11:56,840
I have to answer to all the shareholders.

175
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:57,970
Wouldn't you agree?

176
00:11:58,040 --> 00:11:59,170
That was your doing.

177
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:00,880
You forced them to vote.

178
00:12:01,560 --> 00:12:04,520
You clearly promised
to help me with a bridge loan last week.

179
00:12:04,520 --> 00:12:06,760
That's why I signed that equity guarantee.

180
00:12:06,760 --> 00:12:08,720
That was the final straw.

181
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:10,480
Business is full of ups and downs.

182
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:12,000
You take the risk;
you live with the consequences.

183
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,440
You taught me that.

184
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,160
You forgot?

185
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:20,040
If you jump off,

186
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:23,460
you'll accomplish three things.

187
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:25,520
First,

188
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:28,840
Mrs. Tang's cancer treatment costs

189
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:31,600
will be covered by the insurance company.

190
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:32,360
Second,

191
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:35,000
I will use your son Tang Qi's name

192
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:38,000
to establish an educational fund

193
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:40,400
to guarantee
his studies and life in the US.

194
00:12:40,520 --> 00:12:41,200
Third,

195
00:12:42,520 --> 00:12:44,780
the Tang Group can still survive with me.

196
00:12:46,520 --> 00:12:48,980
So it can still survive
with you around, huh?

197
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:53,120
What a perfect way to get me killed
without getting your hands dirty!

198
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:54,520
Chairman, you're wrong.

199
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:56,480
Legally speaking,

200
00:12:56,920 --> 00:12:58,880
I was never here today.

201
00:12:58,880 --> 00:12:59,600
You.

202
00:13:05,520 --> 00:13:06,280
Doctor.

203
00:13:07,040 --> 00:13:08,880
Sorry, we tried our best.

204
00:13:08,880 --> 00:13:09,810
My condolences.

205
00:13:10,760 --> 00:13:12,000
How could this happen?

206
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:13,280
She was fine yesterday.

207
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:15,160
Didn't you say her condition had improved?

208
00:13:15,160 --> 00:13:16,240
After you left yesterday,

209
00:13:16,240 --> 00:13:17,840
a man surnamed Lu came to her.

210
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:19,480
Later that night, your mother's condition

211
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:20,680
suddenly worsened.

212
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:23,520
It seems she found out
about your father's death.

213
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:29,120
Lu Zhen'an.
